text: Martial Saddier (born October 15, 1969 in Bonneville, Haute-Savoie) is a member of the National Assembly of France. He represents the Haute-Savoie department, and is a member of the Republicans. ==References== Category:1959 births Category:Living people Category:People from Bonneville, Haute-Savoie Category:Union for a Popular Movement politicians Category:The Republicans (France) politicians Category:Deputies of the 12th National Assembly of the French Fifth Republic Category:Deputies of the 13th National Assembly of the French Fifth Republic Category:Deputies of the 14th National Assembly of the French Fifth Republic Category:Deputies of the 15th National Assembly of the French Fifth Republic Category:Regional councillors of Auvergne-Rhône-Alpes
title: Martial Saddier
